title: Keeper - 10" Mini Bungee Cords in Assorted Colors, 8 Pack
description: Keeper manufactures bungee cords that are specially designed to suit particular applications, so the equipment works efficiently and is right for the job. The 10" Mini Bungee Cords are ideal for everyday use around the house or while camping, and can be easily kept handy in workshops of all sizes. Made from premium grade cord with top quality rubber, these bungee cords deliver great durability. Keeper Mini Bungee Cords have UV resistant, woven outer jackets to withstand weather and repeated use. 10" Mini Bungee Cords come in a range of highly visible and eye-catching colors and are the perfect multi-use bungee cord solution. 8 Pack
